  m_Name: TakasuYuuchi
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::CharacterInfo
  characterName: Takasu Yuuchi
  description: The youngest in the family and an avid gamer. He's in a weird position
    when it comes to his family. His sisters never stopped treating him like a kid.
    Especially Katsuko, who's always picking on him. He doesn't find his father very
    remarkable, and his mother is extremely doting towards him. Now in his second
    year of junior high, he goes about his life without a care in the world, only
    needing his video games and gamer friends to keep him company, or so he believes.
